Takunkumin tsaro a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka a Chengdu, China
An samu kwanciyar hankali sosai a wajen ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu na China ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurka suka shirya barin wurin.
An ga manyan motoci uku masu motsi suna shiga ginin, yayin da 'yan sandan kwantar da tarzoma suka yi wa bangarorin biyu luguden wuta a kan titi, wadanda ke kwance da shingayen karfe.
Editan jaridar Global Times ta China ya fada cewa an bai wa ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu sa'o'i 72 su rufe, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga watan Yuli.
China ta tuhumi wasu ma'aikata a ofishin jakadancin Chengdu da "sarrafa ayyukan ba bisa ka'ida ba".
Ba tare da bayar da wani bayani ba, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin wajen China, Wang Wenbin, ya ce irin wannan aiki ya tsoma baki a al'amuran China kuma ya cutar da al'amuran tsaronta.
An bayar da umurnin rufe ofishin jakadancin China a birnin Chengdu a yau Juma'a a zaman ramuwar gayya ga wani umurnin Amurka na rufe ofishin jakadancin China a Houston da ke jihar Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "domin kare dukiyar Amurka da bayanan sirri na Amurkawa".
Yayin da aka rufe ofishin jakadancin China da ke Houston a ranar Juma'a, an ga gungun mutanen da suka bayyana cewa jami'an Amurka ne sun watsar da makaman ta wata kofar baya.
Wang ya fada a ranar Asabar cewa karya yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da diflomasiyya da China za su amsa, ba tare da tantance yadda za a yi hakan ba.
Rufe kan iyakokin ya kara dagula tashin hankalin da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwan da suka shafi kasuwanci da masana'antu da kuma kare hakkin bil'adama.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban mayakan sa-kai a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoto na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ce sama da 'yan Pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a Afghanistan, wadanda akasarinsu 'yan kungiyar Taliban ce da ke da alhakin kai hare-hare kan sojojin Pakistan da farar hula.
Rahoton da kungiyar ta fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar, wadda aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), tana da alaka da kungiyar Taliban ta kungiyar ISIS.
Wasu daga cikin 'yan kungiyar TTP ma sun shiga kungiyar IS, wadda ke da hedikwata a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta mayar da martani ranar Lahadi ga bukatar da kamfanin dillancin labarai na Associated Press ya yi mata ba.
Rahoton ya ce kungiyar IS a Afghanistan, wadda aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta sha fama da hare-hare da jami'an tsaron Afghanistan da kuma dakarun Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wani lokaci da kungiyar Taliban ta Afghanistan ke kai hare-hare.
An shirya rahoton ne ta hanyar tawagar masu sa ido da sanya ido ta Amurka, wadda ke bibiyar kungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a fadin duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa mambobin kungiyar IS a Afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya yi sanyi, har yanzu IS na cikin shugabanninta na kasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar da ke sa ido ta samu bayanai cewa manyan kwamandojin ISIS biyu, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, sun isa Afghanistan daga gabas ta tsakiya.
"Duk da cewa a yankin arewa maso gabashin kasar, (yan kungiyar ISIS) sun kasance suna iya kai hare-hare masu muni a sassa daban-daban na kasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Hakan kuma na da nufin jawo hankalin mayakan Taliban da ke adawa da yarjejeniyar da Amurka ta kulla da su", in ji rahoton, yana mai nuni da wata yarjejeniyar zaman lafiya da Amurka ta kulla da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An yi wannan yarjejeniyar ce domin baiwa Amurka damar kawo karshen hannunta na shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma ta yi kira ga Taliban da ta tabbatar da cewa ba za a yi amfani da yankinta ba ta hanyar 'yan ta'adda.
Ana kuma sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta tabbatar da cewa Taliban ta shiga tsakani a yakin da take yi da IS.
Kashi na biyu kuma watakila mafi muhimmanci na yarjejeniyar shi ne kiran tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da jagoran siyasar Kabul.
A jiya Asabar, ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka ta fitar da wata sanarwa da ke cewa wakilinta na zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake fadawa cikin yankin da ke neman tsalle daga tattaunawar, wadda aka sha dagewa yayin da bangarorin biyu suka yi tur da shirin sakin fursunonin.
Yarjejeniyar ta Amurka ta yi kira ga gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunonin Taliban 5,000 da kuma 'yan Taliban su 'yantar da gwamnati da ma'aikatan soji a matsayin wani abin da ake kira mai kyau da zai ci gaba da tattaunawa.
Har zuwa yanzu dai gwamnati ta ki sakin fursunoni kusan 600 'yan Taliban da ta kira 'yan ta'adda kuma ta ba su 'yanci.
Kungiyar Taliban ta ki amincewa.
"Jam'iyyun sun fi kusa da fara tattaunawar sulhu, muhimmin mataki na gaba da za a dauka na kawo karshen yakin Afghanistan na tsawon shekaru 40", a cewar sanarwar ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka.
"Duk da cewa an samu gagarumin ci gaba a tattaunawar da aka yi a gidan yarin, lamarin na bukatar karin ƙoƙari don warware shi".
Mai magana da yawun kungiyar Taliban a farkon wannan makon ya ce a shirye yake ya yi tattaunawa da shugabannin siyasar Kabul, bayan hutun sallar Idi al-Adha a karshen watan nan, inda ya ce za a kammala sakin fursunonin.
Babban abin da ke damun Pakistan shi ne kasancewar mayakan sa-kai musamman wadanda ke da alaka da kungiyar TTP ko Jamaat-ul-Ahrar ko Lashkar-e-Islam, da kuma wadanda ke da alaka da kungiyar ta Baluchistan Liberation Army, wadda ta dauki alhakin kai hare-haren kunar bakin wake a wannan watan a lardin Sindh da ke kudu maso yammacin kasar da kuma lardin Baluchistan.
An kashe sojojin Pakistan da dama a wannan watan a lardin Baluchistan da ke kudu maso yammacin kasar a yaki da 'yan ta'adda.
TTP ta dauki alhakin daya daga cikin hare-hare mafi muni da aka kai a Pakistan a 2014, lokacin da aka kai wa wata makarantar sojojin Pakistan hari kuma aka kashe mutum 140.
Mafi yawansu dalibai ne, wasu kuma matasa ne kamar 5.
"An kiyasta cewa adadin mayakan Pakistan na kasashen waje a Afghanistan, suna fuskantar barazana ga kasashen biyu, a tsakanin 6,000 zuwa 6,500, yawancinsu suna da TTP", in ji rahoton.
Babban bankin Birtaniya HSBC ya musanta "kafa tarko" ga kamfanin Huawei na China a binciken Amurka - RT Business News
Kamfanin dillancin labarai na London HSBC ya ce ba haka lamarin yake ba, kamar yadda kafofin yada labaran China suka yi iƙirarin yi wa Huawei, wanda hakan ya kai ga kama babban jami'in kamfanin a Canada.
A wani sakon da ya wallafa a WeChat, mai ba da bashi ya ce ayyukansa ba su haifar da binciken Amurka a kan mafi girma a duniya na kayan sadarwa ba, kamar yadda binciken Huawei ya nuna saboda zargin karya takunkumin da Amurka ta kakabawa Iran ya fara da kyau kafin hannun bankin a ƙarshen 2016.
"HSBC ba ta da wani ƙiyayya ga Huawei kuma ba su "frame" Huawei," bankin ya ce a ranar Asabar, ya kara da cewa ba zai taba karkatar da wani facts game da abokan ciniki.
