Barkewar cutar Salmonella ta hallaka mutane 212 a jihohi 23
25 ga Yuli (UPI) - Cibiyar Kula da Cututtuka Masu Yaduwa tana binciken barkewar cutar salmonella wadda ta hallaka mutane 212 a jihohi 23.
A cikin wata sanarwar manema labarai da ta fitar ranar Juma'a CDC ta ruwaito cewa mutum 87 ne suka kamu da cutar tun bayan bullarta a ranar Talata.
Hukumar ta ce mutane sun fara nuna alamun cutar da ke da nasaba da ciwon salmonella, wanda zai iya daukar mako biyu zuwa hudu domin nuna alamun cutar, tsakanin 19 zuwa 11 ga watan Yuli.
Mutane talatin da daya ne aka kwantar a asibiti tun bayan barkewar cutar, amma ba a samu rahoton wadanda suka mutu ba.
A cewar CDC, ba a gano takamaiman tushen nau'in salmonella ba.
Bai bayar da wata shawara ba game da cin abinci ko cin abinci na musamman, ko kuma mai suna 'yan kasuwa da ka iya sayar da kayayyakin da aka gurbata ba.
Oregon ya fi kamuwa da cutar salmonella, tare da kamuwa da cuta 51, tare da Utah bayan kusa da baya da mutum 40 da aka ruwaito sun kamu da cutar.
Salmonella cuta ce, ciwon abinci wanda ke haifar da cututtuka miliyan 1.35, cututtukan asibiti 26,500, da mutuwar 420 a kowace shekara, a cewar CDC.
Mafi yawan alamun kamuwa da cutar salmonella sune zawo, zazzabi, da ciki, wanda zai iya farawa tsakanin sa'o'i shida da kwanaki shida bayan bayyanuwa.
Ciwon yakan wuce kwana hudu zuwa bakwai, kuma yawancin mutane na murmurewa ba tare da magani ba, amma wasu lokuta yana bukatar asibiti.
