Isra'ila ta kama sama da mutum 60,000 a matsayin masu safarar mutane
JERUSALEM (Reuters) - Adadin mutanen da suka kamu da cutar coronavirus a Isra'ila ya kai 60,000 a ranar Asabar yayin da gwamnati ke kokarin shawo kan yaduwar cutar.
Sabbin alkaluman na yau da kullun sun nuna sabbin kamuwa 1,770, wanda ya kawo jimillar wadanda suka kamu da cutar zuwa 60,496, ma'aikatar lafiya ta kasar ta ruwaito.
Da yawan jama'a miliyan tara, Isra'ila ta ba da rahoton adadin wadanda suka mutu 455 daga cutar.
Isra'ila na daya daga cikin kasashe na farko da suka sanya dokar kulle a duk fadin kasar, kuma da farko ta yi nasarar dakile barkewar cutar.
Al'amuran yau da kullum da suka shafi daruruwan mutane sun ragu zuwa ninki biyu.
Damuwa game da matsalar tattalin arziki, gwamnati ta sassauta wadannan takunkumi - da sauri, wasu jami'ai tun bayan da aka amince da su - kuma yawan masu kamuwa da cutar ya karu.
Rufewar ɓangarori daban-daban na tattalin arziƙi ya zurfafa ɓarnar da jama'a ke yi, lamarin da ya haifar da zanga-zangar yau da kullum.
